      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark test cases documented by the vendor.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent vendor-supplied benchmark suite covers laminar and turbulent internal flow cases relevant to blood pump simulation. Published verification reports confirm correct numerical implementation at the required level."
    },
    {
