      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh convergence study must demonstrate that discretization error in hemolysis index QoI is below 5% between successive refinement levels.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the FDA generic pump geometry (coarse: 2.1M, medium: 5.8M, fine: 14.3M cells). Richardson extrapolation yields GCI < 3.8% for the hemolysis index at the worst-case operating point, satisfying the 5% threshold."
