      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) must agree with experimental measurements within ±20% across all assessed operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted NIH values compared against experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. Maximum deviation of 14.7% observed at the 5 L/min / 3800 RPM condition. All points satisfy the ±20% acceptance criterion, with mean absolute error of 9.3%."
